{"tid":472864,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"汪 明 荃 入 行 五 十 週 年 節 目 歌 藝 表 演 重 溫","createTime":"2017-11-18T15:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T09:59:50.000Z","uid":24160,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b52162515859db679bd34d5b638176969d90de76","tid":472864,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:40:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">​<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/3d797d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F3d797d.gif&h=eda1a8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/3d797d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F3d797d.gif&h=eda1a8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/3d797d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F3d797d.gif&h=eda1a8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n汪明荃 - 傾城之戀 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=udfNVz1sHsU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DudfNVz1sHsU&d=SLyg2PkSNY1X1lvnLHb1LjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=2f122fa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=udfNVz1sHsU</a><br />\n<br />\n王祖藍 - 熱咖啡<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YEwmqEhGBwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYEwmqEhGBwg&d=SLyg2PkSNY1X1lvnLHb1LjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c683d77a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YEwmqEhGBwg</a><br />\n<br />\n容祖兒 - 京華春夢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dq6nAMAxu9k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDq6nAMAxu9k&d=SLyg2PkSNY1X1lvnLHb1LjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8258f2c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dq6nAMAxu9k</a><br />\n<br />\n汪明荃 - 銀河<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mJVarFAUogs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmJVarFAUogs&d=SLyg2PkSNY1X1lvnLHb1LjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=edc8787f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mJVarFAUogs</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/c3f3c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fc3f3c2.jpg&h=d7ffd50a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪明荃博士身穿黑色&quot;中門大開&quot;晚裝乘坐駕進入半島酒店會場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/4fc9dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F4fc9dc.jpg&h=9c466b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪博士更與一眾司儀合照，眾人服飾顯得汪氏晚裝簡約而高貴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/840504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F840504.jpg&h=5d81a743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪氏與王浩信合照<br />\n此照更能清楚觀察到汪氏事業線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/de13f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fde13f4.jpg&h=a4b7a8d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/6006d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F6006d2.jpg&h=a6873272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n王浩信難抵阿姐魅力<br />\n害羞得不敢側目凝視<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/d37ace.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fd37ace.jpg&h=f1be7d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪氏換上另一套米色晚裝，盡顯其玲瓏身段<br />\n企喺上等人及一眾甘草演員旁<br />\n更後生成廿年有多，唔似七十歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/d296c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fd296c1.jpg&h=b2c97a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n及後，汪氏再換上閃爆護肩低胸晚裝保護其隨歲月而退化嘅肩膀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其閃爍裝飾簡直閃爆所有重量級嘉賓, 包括胡定欣, Miss Chan Chan, 容祖祖等人<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/209fe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F209fe4.jpg&h=7573fded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/6b0d50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F6b0d50.jpg&h=ec2af2dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/4_img/upload/d411fbc6/20171111/l0eo-fynstfh4874445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2F4_img%2Fupload%2Fd411fbc6%2F20171111%2Fl0eo-fynstfh4874445.jpg&h=ce69249e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪氏亦曾身穿紅色高叉晚裝進出會場<br />\n右邊男子為曾向汪氏問價之高層<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/540/https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/6776b853gy1fka5xap6cqj20zk0qoaji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F6776b853gy1fka5xap6cqj20zk0qoaji.jpg&h=f064a680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿姐真係忙一日換幾套衫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 七十明荃 風韻猶存<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊重溫阿姐演唱會之風采 [5分鐘精華]<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/INS26vhNJdQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FINS26vhNJdQ&d=SLyg2PkSNY1X1lvnLHb1LjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1487c13e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/INS26vhNJdQ</a></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/1229b1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F1229b1.gif&h=0aefb7d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/5c446c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F5c446c.gif&h=487e6e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/f258d0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Ff258d0.gif&h=075f8158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/8ff32e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F8ff32e.gif&h=ce7c5e66&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/11-28-2015/lA5WNN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F11-28-2015%2FlA5WNN.gif&h=92700877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/2d3a9a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F2d3a9a.gif&h=aa0f11eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/2d3a9a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F2d3a9a.gif&h=aa0f11eb&s={SIZE}\" />